      <h1>The Car: VIN 108689</h1>
      <p class="dek">
        A matching-numbers 1959 356A T2 1600 Super Coupe that spent roughly fifty years inside a dry Texas
        machine shop. The objective is not a flawless imitation of a new 356 — it is to preserve the identity
        of this particular car and return it to the road.
      </p>
    </div>

